##############################
### users endpoints

### Get all users (with token)
GET {{apiurl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get all users (FAIL without token)
GET {{apiurl}}/users

### Register new user
POST {{apiurl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "donald555",
  "password": "du12345677ck",
  "email": "donald555@example.com"
}

### Register new user FAIL (email missing)
POST {{apiurl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "donald",
  "password": "duck"
}

### User login
POST {{apiurl}}/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "donald555",
  "password": "du12345677ck"
}

### Get user info by token
GET {{apiurl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Hae käyttäjä ID:llä
GET {{apiurl}}/users/9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Päivitä käyttäjän tiedot
PUT {{apiurl}}/users/7
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "username": "donald3",
  "email": "donald3@example.com"
}

### Poista käyttäjä
DELETE {{apiurl}}/users/9
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

##############################
### Diary entry endpoints

### Get all entries (by user id in token)
GET {{apiurl}}/entries
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get entry by id
GET {{apiurl}}/entries/10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete entry by id
DELETE {{apiurl}}/entries/6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Post new entry
POST {{apiurl}}/entries
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "entry_date": "2026-02-04",
  "mood": "really happy",
  "weight": 66,
  "sleep_hours": 5,
  "notes": "normipäivä"
}

### Modify entry by id
PUT {{apiurl}}/entries/10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "entry_date": "2026-02-04",
  "mood": "tired",
  "weight": 67,
  "sleep_hours": 6,
  "notes": "päivitetty merkintä"
}

##############################
### Blood Pressure endpoints

### Hae kaikki verenpaineet
GET {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Hae mittaukset tietyltä päivältä
GET {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure?date=2026-03-07
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Hae mittaukset aikaväliltä
GET {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure?from=2026-03-01&to=2026-03-05
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Hae yksittäinen mittaus ID:llä
GET {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Lisää uusi mittaus (POST)
POST {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systolic": 135,
  "diastolic": 88,
  "pulse": 22,
  "notes": "Testi HTTP-tiedostosta"
}

### Päivitä mittaus (PUT) - muuta ID (esim. 6) vastaamaan kantaasi
PUT {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure/18
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "systolic": 110,
  "diastolic": 70,
  "pulse": 65,
  "notes": "Päivitetty arvo"
}

### Poista mittaus (DELETE) - muuta ID vastaamaan kantaasi
DELETE {{apiurl}}/bloodpressure/18
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

